{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"nameNarration":"吉良手鞠","narration":"在历史研究社成立的几天后","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"narration":"我们在这个休息处@沉迷于各自喜爱的事@度过了轻松愉快的时间"},{"chara":[{"id":304001},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narration":"但我还是心存疑惑"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"id":304001}],"nameLeft":"吉良手鞠","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"说到底……我的魔法究竟是什么呢？"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"古町美仓","textRight":"你还在想这件事啊。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"古町你就不在意吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"三穗野星罗","textLeft":"古町学姐也不知道自己的魔法吧。"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"嗯，但是总有一天会知道的。"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textRight":"所以我反倒不太明白@为什么你会那么在意。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"吉良手鞠","textLeft":"实现愿望的恶魔……@实现愿望的物神……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"在民间故事、戏曲和微小说里，@经常会出现诸如此类的主题。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"它不仅立马实现了古町的愿望。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"也让三穗野获得了简单易懂的魔法。"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":300}],"textRight":"是啊。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"但就我的愿望来说……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"如果我不发表作品，就无法实现愿望。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"所以也一直不明白@我作为魔法少女所拥有的力量。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三穗野星罗","textRight":"但肯定是会有什么的吧？"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"嗯，这倒没错……"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304001}],"textLeft":"可我一直搞不清楚这件事，@所以我也很烦躁。"},{"textLeft":"就像是读了一本被撕掉@最后一页的小说一样……"},{"chara":[{"id":303901,"motion":300}],"textRight":"这样啊。"},{"chara":[{"id":303901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"用作品来说的话，@就会有种很不舒服的感觉吧！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"没错。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"明明已经到了最后关头……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"眼看着就要有方向了……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"古町美仓","textRight":"方向吗……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"是的。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"之前我也说过。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"我的魔法应该是@和话语有关的东西……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"……@……"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textRight":"吉良的话语……"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21021.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"吉良手鞠","textLeft":"我是不太想加入……毕竟我很怕生。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textLeft":"我还是想维持三人合作的状态。"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21021.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"nameLeft":"吉良手鞠","textLeft":"不好意思，古町，@我想冒昧地问一句……","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"nameRight":"古町美仓","textRight":"没关系，我也习惯了。@[chara:303801:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:303801:cheek_0][chara:303801:motion_1][chara:303801:lipSynch_1]所以你有什么问题呢？"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"你不觉得我们@需要一个地方休息吗？"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textRight":"嗯……","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"难道你有头绪了吗？"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"嗯，总觉得我们最近@都照着吉良说的话……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三穗野星罗","textRight":"照着学姐的话？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"古町美仓","textRight":"抱歉，没什么，是我多心了。"},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textRight":"我有什么新发现会跟你们说的。"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"是吗……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"我还以凭为你的观察力@还能发现点什么呢……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三穗野星罗","textRight":"对了，吉良学姐今天在看什么书呢？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"最近几天我都一直在看镜花全集。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":400}],"textRight":"[chara:303901:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]咦？！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"古町美仓","textRight":"你居然和之前看的一样？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"三穗野星罗","textLeft":"是的！真叫人意外啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"古町美仓","textRight":"吉良的喜好还真是让人猜不透啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303901,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"三穗野星罗","textLeft":"嗯，好有趣呀！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"吉良手鞠","textLeft":"嗯……"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textLeft":"继古町之后，@连三穗野也来问我这个问题了……"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3040_00_05","textHome":"…现实比起小说还要奇幻，吗"}],"nameCenter":"吉良手鞠","textCenter":"现实永远要比小说更加离奇吗……","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}